title: [Cypress Walk, Plaza]
description: The bustling plaza is ringed by prosperous homes, their wrought iron gates decorated with climbing vines and blooming roses.  On the north side of the stone circle stands a small wooden building, its weathered appearance a gentle contrast to the stately whitewash of the surrounding homes.  Faint strains of music drift from its swinging doors.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
